				<wikidot:authorName>Prototype_Toaster</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3512728</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The description was confusing and hard to follow at times. However, I was a big fan of the Addendum and dialogues and liked the ending.</p> <p>One thing that I always like in skips is the pictures in it. This skip has some very good images with it. Very /comfy/.</p> <p>So +1 for the dialogues and story. But that description needs some work so it can be read easier</p> 
				 	]]>
